en-US.title: Family Health Centers of San Diego
en-US.description: Committed to providing affordable and high-quality health care to everyone, especially the uninsured, low-income, and medically underserved individuals. With a list of comprehensive services, it caters to various groups including the transgender community. It provides transgender health services ensuring a safe, welcoming environment promoting essential health needs.

address: 823 Gateway Center Way, San Diego, CA 92102, USA
